import * as React from 'react' import Title from './components/title_bar' import Navbar from './components/nav_bar' import './pageTwo.css' export default function Objectives(){ const [Lang,SetLang] = React.useState('EN'); let LangEN,LangDE; if(Lang === 'EN'){ LangEN = 'block' LangDE = 'none' } else if (Lang === 'DE'){ LangDE='block' LangEN='none' } return(
<Navbar onUpdate = {(value:string) => SetLang(value)} pg_Objectives='4px solid red'/> <div className='txt_box'> <h1 style={{display:LangEN}}>Objective and purpose</h1> <h1 style={{display:LangDE}}>Zweck und ziel</h1> <hr></hr> <p><b>The purpose of the club is:</b> <ul> <li>to encourage contact between the international workforce of the research center (Forschungszentrum Jülich GmbH) and the residents of Jülich, to organisations of the same type, both at home and abroad. </li> <li>to provide assistance to all club members. </li> </ul> To this end, the club will organise informative, cultural and social gatherings to lead people towards thoughts of tolerance and understanding. The club's exclusive and immediate purpose is to benifit the community (im Sinne der Gemeinnützigkeitsverordnung vom 24. Dezember, 1953). </p> </div> </div> ) }
